 Cui Hongfang , 73 , died in front of horrified family members and holidaymakers after she was knocked over by the 38-year-old Canadian woman .
Mrs Hongfong , from Heilongjiang Province in north-eastern China , struck her head in a tragedy that was ruled an accident by police .
The victim 's family filed a civil lawsuit against the tourist , Debra Fortin and ruled the death an accident .